// TODO: Tune gap_pct per timeframe (4H may need 3–5%, 15m needs 1.5–2%)
// TODO: Add volume filter — entry candle should have above-avg volume (short squeeze confirmation)
// TODO: Add inverted H&S pattern detection as bonus entry signal
// TODO: Add partial take-profit at first gap, trail remainder above 21 SMA
// TODO: Test on BTC 4H, BTC 15m, and altcoins separately
// TODO: Consider adding ATR-based gap threshold instead of fixed %
